<div class="fy_zcbj">

    <div class="fy_sqw">
    	<h3>陕西省中医医院病理信息管理与质控系统采购项目  中标（成交）结果公告   </h3>
      <i>发布时间：2025-04-30 22:25   来源：   浏览次数：<script type='text/javascript' src='/web/news_checknum.rt?contentId=14985&channlId=278'></script></i>
       
        <div style="color:#000000;">
      		<p><br/></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">项目名称：陕西省中医医院病理信息管理与质控系统采购项目</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">采购结果</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px"><img src="/uploadfile/ueditor/image/20250430/1746023142513040150.png" title="1746023142513040150.png" alt="1d3e2a229a3cae2d174edd2606be885.png" width="756" height="135" style="width: 756px; height: 135px;"/></span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">三、评标专家（公开招标）名单：</span></p><p style=";text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">郝正庆、梁</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋">力、席一凡、陈</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋">鹏、高</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋">峰（采购人代表）</span></span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">四、公告期限　</span></p><p style=";text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">自本公告发布之日起</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1个工作日。</span></span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">五、凡对本公告内容提出询问，请按以下方式联系。</span></p><p style=";text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">采购项目联系人：赵老师</span></p><p style=";text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">联系方式：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">029-87251591&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=";text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">采购单位地址：西安市莲湖区西华门</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">4号陕西省中医医院</span></span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">六、各有关当事人若对本公告有异议，请按《中华人民共和国政府采购法》第五十二条之有关规定执行。</span></p><p style=";text-indent:405px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=";text-indent:405px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:384px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">资产管理办公室</span></p><p style="text-indent:384px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">2025年4月30日</span></p><p><br/></p>
